{"thag4.2:0.1":"Theragatha 4.2 ","thag4.2:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","thag4.2:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag4.2:0.4":"Bhaguttheragatha ","thag4.2:1.1":"“Aham middhena pakato, ","thag4.2:1.2":"vihara upanikkhamim; ","thag4.2:1.3":"Cankamam abhiruhanto, ","thag4.2:1.4":"tattheva papatim chama. ","thag4.2:2.1":"Gattani parimajjitva, ","thag4.2:2.2":"punaparuyha cankamam; ","thag4.2:2.3":"Cankame cankamim soham, ","thag4.2:2.4":"ajjhattam susamahito. ","thag4.2:3.1":"Tato me manasikaro, ","thag4.2:3.2":"yoniso udapajjatha; ","thag4.2:3.3":"Adinavo paturahu, ","thag4.2:3.4":"nibbida samatitthatha. ","thag4.2:4.1":"Tato cittam vimucci me, ","thag4.2:4.2":"passa dhammasudhammatam; ","thag4.2:4.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thag4.2:4.4":"katam buddhassa sasanan”ti. ","thag4.2:4.5":"… Bhagutthero …. "}